column4: Oakwood Village Library and Arts Centre

column1: Note: This new internal measure replaces Active Cardholders and Registered Cardholders reported in 2017 and earlier. Cardholders captures customers whose records have reported activity in the past 2 years (2017 and 2018).
Activities include: checkout, renewal, check-in, billing, payment, placing a hold, a new registration, and login authentication to access some electronic databases.
